OL,3,C'I was blamed for my baby's death':
OL,4,CMums speak out on maternity care
OL,6,FNow three women have spoken
OL,7,Fexclusively to ITV News Central about
OL,8,Ftheir experiences - as they call for
OL,9,Fthe government to step in.
OL,11,F'My whole world came crashing down'
OL,13,FKatie Russell's daughter Poppy died in
OL,14,FShropshire in 2021, just 12 hours
OL,15,Fafter she was born.
OL,17,FFoetal monitoring was part of Katie's
OL,18,Fbirth plan, and she told ITV News
OL,19,FCentral that this was needed as
OL,20,F"frequently as possible".
