OL,3,C'I was blamed for my baby's death':
OL,4,CMums speak out on maternity care
OL,6,F"It didn't seem that the monitoring
OL,7,Fwas that regular during the actual
OL,8,Fwater birth, but as my first child, I
OL,9,Fdidn't know any different," she said.
OL,11,FAfter a prolonged labour, Katie needed
OL,12,Fan emergency caesarean section. But it
OL,13,Fwas too late. Poppy lived for just 12
OL,14,Fhours.
OL,16,FWatch Katie's story...
OL,18,FShe said: "My whole world came
OL,19,Fcrashing down. It was the worst
OL,20,Ffeeling anyone could ever experience."
