OL,3,C'I was blamed for my baby's death':
OL,4,CMums speak out on maternity care
OL,6,F"Our house was set up to welcome a new
OL,7,Fbaby and having to go home without
OL,8,Fthat child was just the worst thing in
OL,9,Fthe world," she added.
OL,11,FAn inquest found Poppy's death was
OL,12,Fpreventable, as staff had failed to
OL,13,Fproperly monitor her heart rate.
OL,15,FThe coroner dismissed claims by the
OL,16,Ftrust that Katie had declined
OL,17,Fmonitoring.
