OL,3,C'I was blamed for my baby's death':
OL,4,CMums speak out on maternity care
OL,6,FShe said: "There were many things that
OL,7,FI couldn't believe were said about me,
OL,8,Fand they were really hurtful. You
OL,9,Fthink it's not bad enough that your
OL,10,Fchild's died? You're now being blamed
OL,11,Ffor it."
OL,13,FAfterwards, Katie and her husband Neil
OL,14,Fbegan fighting for answers.
OL,16,F"It just felt like we were fighting an
OL,17,Fuphill battle and we were on our own,"
OL,18,Fshe said.
