OL,6,FShe said: "We are truly sorry. We have
OL,7,Fmade many improvements to our services
OL,8,Fsince 2021, but Mr and Mrs Russell's
OL,9,Fexperience shows us that we have
OL,10,Ffurther to go."
OL,12,F'I just wanted to get out alive with
OL,13,Fmy baby'
OL,15,FDivina Johnson had a normal pregnancy
OL,16,Fand assumed when her waters broke at
OL,17,F41 weeks, that labour would be the
OL,18,Fsame.
OL,20,FHowever, she was horrified by the care
OL,21,Fthat she received.
