OL,3,C'I was blamed for my baby's death':
OL,4,CMums speak out on maternity care
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News Central, Divina
OL,7,Fsaid: "I was probably in that fog,
OL,8,Fdazed shock for a year of just
OL,9,Fflashbacks, nightmares.
OL,11,F"I was told that I was taking a long
OL,12,Ftime. It felt like a problem, that we
OL,13,Fneed to just get this woman to have
OL,14,Fher baby and to move her on. There was
OL,15,Fnever communication about what was
OL,16,Fhappening or why this was happening."
OL,18,FWatch Divina's story...
