OL,3,C'I was blamed for my baby's death':
OL,4,CMums speak out on maternity care
OL,6,FDivina was told that she needed an
OL,7,Fepidural, which she says left her in
OL,8,Fthe worst pain she has ever known.
OL,10,F"I kind of felt like it was an out-of-
OL,11,Fbody experience. I feel like I could
OL,12,Fsee myself just shaking in a type of
OL,13,Fpain that I've never experienced
OL,14,Fbefore and I know that (the midwife)
OL,15,Fhad hit a nerve," she said.
OL,17,F"I remember when I was just lying
OL,18,Fthere, her laughing at me and saying
OL,19,F'Oh people don't normally act that way
OL,20,Fwhen I give them an epidural'."
