OL,3,C'I was blamed for my baby's death':
OL,4,CMums speak out on maternity care
OL,6,FDivina continued to have shooting
OL,7,Fpains and spasms across her body.
OL,9,FAfter nearly two days in labour, she
OL,10,Fwas given a caesarean section.
OL,12,FShe said: "I remember feeling so numb,
OL,13,Fand not just physically because I was
OL,14,Fnumb, but just emotionally. I remember
OL,15,Fjust thinking, 'Can anyone see me?
OL,16,FDoes anyone see, me?'"
OL,18,FDivina says she felt as though no one
OL,19,Fcared for her, and that what was
OL,20,Fsupposed to be a caring and nurturing
OL,21,Fexperience, was not.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/18
