OL,3,C'I was blamed for my baby's death':
OL,4,CMums speak out on maternity care
OL,6,F"I didn't expect to get good
OL,7,Ftreatment, I didn't expect to be cared
OL,8,Ffor. I just wanted to get out alive
OL,9,Fwith my baby, because that was the
OL,10,Flevel of expectation that I had," she
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FAs a result of the treatment she
OL,14,Freceived, Divina struggled to bond
OL,15,Fwith her baby after birth. She's since
OL,16,Fhad two healthy babies but said the
OL,17,Ftrauma often comes back.
OL,19,F'I was given an adoption leaflet'
